  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Controller. Your beast form gives you access to powers that provide control at close range, while your humanoid form allows you to hinder your opponents from a distance. Depending on your choice of class features and powers, you might lean toward either leader or striker as a secondary role.</p><p><strong>Power Source:</strong> : Primal. You have gained your powers through a careful study of and communion with the natural world.</p><p><strong>Key Abilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Wisdom</p></li><li><p>Dexterity</p></li><li><p>Constitution</p></li></ul><p><strong>Armour Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.GwsMGFG3ogxFrvmJ]{Cloth armor (basic clothing)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.lnYMh2YvKedWTpCt]{Leather armor}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.kVD04UqK9Yx6GeRA]{Hide armor}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.kjW9S8gIQ0LBMF53]{Simple Melee Weapons}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.G50MDDGV8v1NRT9u]{Simple Ranged Weapons}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Implements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.vu6lVEBahrmh5L3O]{Staff}</p></li><li><p>Totems</p></li></ul><p><strong>Bonus to Defences:</strong></p><ul><li><p>+1 Reflex</p></li><li><p>+1 Will</p></li></ul><p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:: [[12]] + Con Score</strong></p><p><strong>Hit Points per Level Gained: [[5]]</strong></p><p><strong>Base Healing Surges per Day: [[7]] + Con Mod</strong></p><p><strong>Skill Training; </strong>Nature, choose three more from the following list:</p><ul><li><p>Arcana (Int)</p></li><li><p>Athletics (Str)</p></li><li><p>Diplomacy (Cha)</p></li><li><p>Endurance (Con)</p></li><li><p>Heal (Wis)</p></li><li><p>History (Int)</p></li><li><p>Insight (Wis)</p></li><li><p>Perception (Wis)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Class Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Balance of Nature</p></li><li><p>Ritual Casting</p></li><li><p>Wild Shape</p></li></ul><p><strong>Choose one of the following Primal Aspect Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Primal Guardian</p></li><li><p>Primal Predator</p></li></ul>",
